“湖北超3000名医护人员感染”。
"Hubei super 3000 medical personnel infected."
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 邵克3月6日下午，国务院新闻办公室在湖北武汉举行新闻发布会，请中央指导组相关成员介绍新冠肺炎疫情防控救治进展情况，并答记者问。
Shao Pai News Correspondent Shao Kek held a press conference in Wuhan, Hubei Province on March 6, asking relevant members of the Central Steering Group to introduce the progress of prevention and treatment of the new crown pneumonia and answer questions.
有记者提问，疫情发生以来，有不少医护人员感染，是什么导致这种情况的发生？另外，采取了哪些措施保护前线医护人员的安全？中央指导组成员、国务院副秘书长丁向阳介绍，湖北省有超过3000名医护人员被感染，其中40%是在医院感染的，60%在社区，均为湖北当地的医务人员，而且大多是非传染科的医生。
A reporter asked if there had been many cases of infection among medical staff since the outbreak. What measures have been taken to protect the safety of frontline medical personnel? Besides, over 3,000 medical workers in Hubei Province have been infected, 40% of them in hospitals and 60% in the community.
丁向阳说：“如果说原因，我觉得初期是大家对病毒的认识不足，防控知识缺乏。
Ding Xiangyang said: "If the reason, I think the initial stage is the lack of awareness of the virus, lack of knowledge of prevention and control.
在这次疫情防控中，也有多位医务人员因为感染发病而献出了宝贵的生命，这让我们所有的人都为之惋惜和悲痛。
In this epidemic prevention and control, there are also many medical staff because of the outbreak of the loss of precious lives, which we all regret and grief.
